  Instruction dump:
  419e0018 2f83ffff 419e00bc 2f83ffea 409e00cc 4800001c 0fe00000 3c62ff96
  39000001 39400000 386386d0 480000c4 <0fe00000> 3ce20003 39000001 3c62ff96
